            function initTemplateLevel(templateWrapper, level, template) {
                var question = level.question;
                if (question) {
                    var answers = question.answers;
                    if (answers) {
                        var options = "<option value='' disabled selected>\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82</option>";
                        for (var i = 0; i < answers.length; i++) {
                            options += "<option data-index='" + i + "' value='" + answers[i].value + "'>" + answers[i].value + "</option>";
                        }
                        var questionDOM = "<div id=t_row_question_" + question.id + " class='row'>" +
                            "<div class='col l12 s12 m12'><p class='template-question' style='margin: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);'>" + question.name + (question.required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "") +"</p>" +
                            "<div class='input-field'>" +
                            "<select class='t_control browser-default "+ (question.required ? "required" : "") + "' " + (question.template ? 'data-template = "' + question.template + '"' : 'data-name = "' + encodeURIComponent(question.name) + '"') + " id=t_select_question_" + question.id + ">" + options + "</select>" +
                            "</div>" +
                            "</div>" +
                            "</div>";
                        templateWrapper.append(questionDOM);
                        var currentQuestion = $("#t_select_question_" + question.id);
                        currentQuestion.material_select();
                        currentQuestion.change(function () {

                            if(!$(this).hasClass('question-valid')){
                                $(this).addClass('question-valid');
                            }

                            //saveDraftToObject(router);

                            var questionId = question.id;
                            var answer = answers[$(this).find('option:selected').data("index")];

                            var oldQuestions = $("#t_row_question_" + questionId).nextAll();

                            if (answer.serviceId) {
                                serviceId = answer.serviceId;
                            } else {
                                if (oldQuestions.length > 0) {
                                    serviceIdCandidate = undefined;
                                    searchNearServiceId(questionId, template);
                                    if (serviceIdCandidate) {
                                        serviceId = serviceIdCandidate;
                                    } else {
                                        serviceId = rootServiceId;
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            oldQuestions.remove();

                            //console.log(serviceId);
                            initTemplateLevel(templateWrapper, answer, template);
                            var fileRequiredCounter = $('.file-required').length;
                            if(fileRequiredCounter > 0){
                                $('.ajax-file-upload').next('span').find('span').text('\xD0\x94\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B').append('<span style="color: red"> *</span>');
                            } else {
                                $('.ajax-file-upload').next('span').find('span').text('\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B');
                            }
                        })
                    } else {
                        //console.log("Bad question")
                    }
                } else {
                    var fields = level.fields;
                    if (fields && fields.length > 0) {
                        fieldGenerator(fields, templateWrapper);
                    }
                }

                function searchNearServiceId(questionId, template) {

                    var question = template.question;
                    if (question && question.answers) {
                        if (question.id == questionId) {
                            serviceId = serviceIdCandidate;
                        } else {
                            for (var i = 0; i < question.answers.length; i++) {
                                if (question.answers[i].serviceId && question.answers[i].question) {
                                    serviceIdCandidate = question.answers[i].serviceId;
                                    searchNearServiceId(question.answers[i].question.id, question.answers[i])
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0
            var newContactBtn = $("#new_contact");
            newContactBtn.tooltip({
                delay: 50,
                tooltip: "\xD0\x94\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8",
                position: "bottom"
            });
            var newContactContainer = $("#new_contact_container");
            var contactSelector = $("#contact");

            //\xD0\x9D\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0
            newContactBtn.click(function () {
                if (newContactContainer.hasClass("hide")) {
                    newContactContainer.removeClass("hide");
                }
                if (contactSelector.length) {
                    contactSelector.val(0);
                    contactSelector.material_select();
                }
            });

            if (contactSelector.length) {
                contactSelector.change(function () {
                    if (!newContactContainer.hasClass("hide")) {
                        newContactContainer.addClass("hide");
                    }
                });
            }

            //\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x81 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC Fileupload
            var fileIdArray = [];
            var maxFileSize = {max:10485760, current:0};
            $("#fileuploader").uploadFile({
                maxFileCount: 6,
                maxFileSize: 10485760,
                dragDropStr: "<span><span style='margin-left: 15px;'>\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B</span></span>",
                showDelete: true,
                url: "api/ticket/file/",
                fileName: "files",
                sequential: false,
                sequentialCount: 6,
                enctype: "multipart/form-data",
                deleteCallback: function (obj) {
                    var fileName = toTranslit(obj[0].name);
                    maxFileSize.current -= maxFileSize[fileName];
                    delete maxFileSize[fileName];
                    //console.log(maxFileSize);
                    $.ajax({
                        url: 'api/ticket/file/' + obj[0].id,
                        type: 'DELETE'
                    }).always(function () {
                        for (var i = 0; i < fileIdArray.length; i++) {
                            if (obj[0].id === fileIdArray[i]) {
                                fileIdArray.splice(i, 1);
                                break;
                            }
                        }
                    })
                },
                onSelect:function (files) {
                    //debugger;
                    var totalSize = 0;
                    $.each(files, function (i, file) {
                        totalSize += file.size;
                    });
                    if(maxFileSize.current + totalSize > maxFileSize.max){
                        $messageModal.find('p').text('\xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x89\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C 10 \xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD1\x82');
                        $messageModal.find('a').removeAttr('href');
                        $messageModal.modal('open');
                        //console.log(maxFileSize);
                        return false;
                    } else {
                        $.each(files, function (i, file) {
                            maxFileSize[toTranslit(file.name)] = file.size
                        });

                        maxFileSize.current += totalSize;
                        //console.log(maxFileSize);
                        return true;
                    }
                },
                onSuccess:function(files,data)
                {
                    Materialize.toast('\xD0\xA4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB \xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD', 3000);
                    fileIdArray.push(data[0].id);
                    $('.ajax-upload-dragdrop').removeClass('red-dotted-border');
                },
                onError: function(files,status,errMsg,pd)
                {
                    Materialize.toast('\xD0\x9E\xD1\x88\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 ', 3000);
                }
            });

            //\xD0\xA1\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x87, \xD0\xB3\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD1\x83\xD1\x8E\xD1\x89\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F
            function fieldGenerator(fields, templateWrapper) {
                var templateForm = "";
                for (var i = 0; i < fields.length; i++) {
                    var answ = fields[i].template ? 'data-template = "' + fields[i].template + '"' : 'data-name = "' + encodeURIComponent(fields[i].name) + '"';
                    switch (fields[i].type) {
                        case "TEXT":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'>" +
                                "   <div class='col l12 s12 m12'><p class='template-question'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "") +"</p>" +
                                "       <input class='t_control " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + " id=t_text_" + fields[i].id + " type='text'>" +
                                "   </div>" +
                                "</div>";
                            break;
                        case "SELECT":
                            var options = "<option value='' disabled selected>\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82</option>";
                            for (var j = 0; j < fields[i].values.length; j++) {
                                options += "<option value='" + fields[i].values[j] + "'>" + fields[i].values[j] + "</option>";
                            }
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'>" +
                                "<div class='col l12 s12 m12'>" +
                                "   <p class='template-question'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "") + "</p>" +
                                "   <div class='input-field'>" +
                                "       <select class='browser-default t_control " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + " id=t_select_" + fields[i].id + ">" + options + "</select>" +
                                "   </div>" +
                                "</div>" +
                                "</div>";
                            break;
                        case "MULTI_SELECT":
                            var multipleOptions = "<option value='' disabled selected>\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82</option>";
                            for (var z = 0; z < fields[i].values.length; z++) {
                                multipleOptions += "<option value='" + z + "'>" + fields[i].values[z] + "</option>";
                            }
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'>" +
                                "<div class='col l12 s12 m12'>" +
                                "   <p class='template-question'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "") + "</p>" +
                                "   <div class='input-field'>" +
                                "       <select multiple style='height: 100px;' class='t_control " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + " id=t_multiple_" + fields[i].id + ">" + multipleOptions + "</select>" +
                                "   </div>" +
                                "   </div>" +
                                "</div>";
                            break;
                        case "CHECKBOX":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row checkbox-row'>" +
                                "<div class='input-field col l12 s12 m12'>" +
                                "   <input class='t_control t_check' " + answ + " type='checkbox' id=t_check_" + fields[i].id + ">" +
                                "<label style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);' for='t_check_" + fields[i].id + "'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "") + "</label>" +
                                "</div></div>";
                            break;
                        case "DATE":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'>" +
                                "<div class='input-field col l12 s12 m12'>" +
                                "   <p class='template-question'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "")  + "</p>" +
                                "   <input placeholder='\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x83' class='t_control datepicker " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + " id=t_data_" + fields[i].id + " type='date'>" +
                                "</div>" +
                                "</div>";
                            break;
                        case "DATE_RANG":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'>" +
                                "<div class='col l12 m12 s12'>" +
                                "   <p class='template-question'>" + fields[i].name + (fields[i].required ? "<span style='color: red;'> *</span>" : "")  + "</p>" +
                                "</div>" +
                                "<div class='col l6 m6 s12 input-field'>" +
                                "   <p style='margin: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);'>\xD0\xA1</p>" +
                                "   <input data-id='" + fields[i].id + "' class='t_data_range t_control datepicker " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + " id='t_datarange_left_" + fields[i].id + "' type='date'>" +
                                "</div>" +
                                "<div class='col l6 m6 s12 input-field'>" +
                                "   <p style='margin: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);'>\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE</p>" +
                                "   <input data-id='" + fields[i].id + "' class='t_data_range t_control datepicker " + (fields[i].required ? "required" : "") + "' " + answ + "  id='t_datarange_right_" + fields[i].id + "' type='date'>" +
                                "</div>" +
                                "   <div class='datarange_error ee-hidden col l12 s12 m12'>" +
                                "   <p style='color: red; margin: 0;'>\xD0\x94\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x87\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB6\xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB1\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8C\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B \xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0!</p>" +
                                "</div></div>";
                            break;
                        case "INFO":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'><div class='col l12 m12 s12'><p class='template-question" + (fields[i].required ? " alert-ticket-message info-required" : "")+  "'>" + fields[i].name + "</p></div></div>";
                            break;
                        case "FILE":
                            templateForm += "<div id='t_row_field_" + fields[i].id + "' class='row'><div class='col l12 m12 s12'><p class='template-question file-required'>" + fields[i].name + "</p></div></div>";
                            break;
                    }
                }
                templateWrapper.append(templateForm);
                requiredDescriptionCheck();

                var $tControl = $('input.t_control');
                $tControl.unbind('change.special');
                $tControl.on('change.special', function () {
                    //saveDraftToObject(router);
                    if(!$(this).hasClass('question-valid') && $(this).val() !== ""){
                        $(this).addClass('question-valid');
                    } else {
                        $(this).removeClass('question-valid');
                    }
                });

                var $StControl = $('select.t_control');
                $StControl.unbind('change.special');
                $StControl.on('change.special', function () {
                    //saveDraftToObject(router);
                    if($(this).hasClass('question-valid') && ($(this).val() !== "" || $(this).val() !== [])){
                        if($(this).hasClass('initialized')){
                            $(this).prevAll('input').addClass('question-valid');
                        } else {
                            $(this).addClass('question-valid');
                        }
                    } else {
                        if($(this).hasClass('initialized')){
                            $(this).prevAll('input').removeClass('question-valid');
                        } else {
                            $(this).removeClass('question-valid');
                        }
                    }
                });

                var fileRequiredCounter = $('.file-required').length;
                if(fileRequiredCounter > 0){
                    //console.log('TIME TO REQUIRE FILES AMIGO (BROWSER)');
                    $('.ajax-file-upload').next('span').find('span').text('\xD0\x94\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B').append('<span style="color: red"> *</span>');;
                } else {
                    $('.ajax-file-upload').next('span').find('span').text('\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B');
                }

                $('.datepicker').pickadate({
                    selectMonths: true, // Creates a dropdown to control month
                    selectYears: 15 // Creates a dropdown of 15 years to control year,
                });

                $('.t_data_range').change(function () {

                    var currentDataRangeId = $(this).data('id');
                    var currentDataRange = $('.t_data_range[data-id=' + currentDataRangeId + ']');
                    var dateParts = currentDataRange[0].value.split(".");
                    var dateObject = new Date(dateParts[2], dateParts[1] - 1, dateParts[0]);
                    var leftValue = dateObject;
                    dateParts = currentDataRange[1].value.split(".");
                    dateObject = new Date(dateParts[2], dateParts[1] - 1, dateParts[0]);
                    var rightValue = dateObject;
                    if (rightValue !== "" && leftValue !== "" && (rightValue < leftValue)) {
                        currentDataRange.each(function () {
                            if (!$(this).hasClass('invalid')) $(this).addClass('invalid');
                            var rangeErr = $('.datarange_error');
                            if (rangeErr.hasClass('ee-hidden')) rangeErr.removeClass('ee-hidden');
                        });
                    } else {
                        currentDataRange.each(function () {
                            if ($(this).hasClass('invalid')) $(this).removeClass('invalid');
                            var rangeErr = $('.datarange_error');
                            if (!rangeErr.hasClass('ee-hidden')) rangeErr.addClass('ee-hidden');
                        });
                    }
                });

                $('select').material_select();
            }

            //\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83
            $('#ticket_send').submit(function (event) {
                event.preventDefault();

                var themeSelector = $('#ticket_name'),
                    inventoryNum = $('#inventory_num'),
                    contactMail = $('#task_mail'),
                    contactPhone = $('#task_phone'),
                    contactSelector = $("#contact"),
                    ticketDescription = $('#ticket_description'),
                    placeSelector = $('#placeFor');

                //\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x84\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E \xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0

                var templateFields = $('select.t_control, input.t_control');
                var templateOutput = getResultFromField(templateFields);

                if (templateOutput && templateOutput.length > 0) {
                    templateOutput = (ticketDescription.val() === "" ? "" : "\\n\\n") + templateOutput.join("\\n");
                } else templateOutput = "";

                var isFileRequired = false;
                var testText = $('.ticket-breabcrumbs').text();

                if (formValidation(themeSelector, placeSelector, inventoryNum, contactPhone, ticketDescription, templateFields, fileIdArray, isInventory, isFileRequired)) {

                    $('#add_ticket_set').prop('disabled', true);
                    var progress = $('#new_ticket_progress');
                    if (progress.hasClass('ee-hidden')) progress.removeClass('ee-hidden');
                    var ticket = {
                        text: ticketDescription.val() + templateOutput,
                        header: themeSelector.children(':selected').text(),
                        ticketStateId: 0,
                        serviceId: serviceId,
                        files: fileIdArray,
                        inventoryNumberId: inventoryNum.val(),
                        shopId: shopId
                    };

                    //\xD0\x98\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA
                    /* var $inventarySelector = $("#inventarySelector");
                    if ($inventarySelector.val() !== null) {
                        ticket.inventoryNumberId = $inventarySelector.val();
                    }

                    if (router.args["user"]) {
                        ticket.userId = router.args["user"];
                    }
                    if (contactSelector.length && contactSelector.val()) {
                        ticket.contact = {
                            id: contactSelector.val()
                        };
                    } else {
                        /*ticket.contact = {
                            fullName: "\xD0\x90\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xA1\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B\xD1\x88\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB2",
                            email: "a.smyshliaev@gmail.com",
                            phone: "+7 977 833 44 86"
                        };*/
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "POST",
                        url: 'api/ticket/',
                        dataType: 'json',
                        contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                        data: JSON.stringify(ticket)
                    }).done(function (data) {
                        if(role === "master") {
                            $messageModal.find('p').html('\xD0\x9D\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82 INC_' + data.id +' \xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD<br>' +
                                '\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB2 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0 ' +
                                '<a class="modal-action modal-close" href="/#ticket/' + data.id + '">\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0</a>');
                        } else {
                            $messageModal.find('p').html('\xD0\x9D\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 <a class="modal-action modal-close" href="#ticket/' + data.id + '">\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82 INC_'+ data.id + '</a> \xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD');
                        }
                        $messageModal.find('a').last().attr('href', '/');
                        $messageModal.modal('open');
                        $('#ticket_description').val("");
                        //\xD0\xA3\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE
                        $('.modal-overlay').unbind('click');

                        $.removeCookie('ticket.draft.' + router.path[1]);
                    }).fail(function (error) {
                        if (!progress.hasClass('ee-hidden')) progress.addClass('ee-hidden');

                        $messageModal.find('p').text(error.responseJSON.message);
                        $messageModal.find('a').attr('href', '/');
                        $messageModal.modal('open');
                        //console.log(JSON.parse(error.responseText).code + ' ' + JSON.parse(error.responseText).message);
                        $('#add_ticket_set').prop('disabled', false);
                    });
                }
            });
        })
    }
}

//\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD1\x86\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD1\x84\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
function formValidation(themeSelector, placeSelector, inventoryNum, contactPhone, ticketDescription, templateFields, fileIdArray, isInventory, isFileRequired) {
    var fileSelector = $('#fileuploader').find('> div:first-child');
    var $messageModal = $('#messageModal');
    var fields = [];
    var isValid = true;

    var removeThemeSelectorInvalidClassHandler = function(){themeSelector.parent().find('.material_like').toggleClass('invalid-textarea', false);};
    themeSelector.unbind('change', removeThemeSelectorInvalidClassHandler);
    themeSelector.on('change', removeThemeSelectorInvalidClassHandler);

    /*var removeTicketDescriptionInvalidClassHandler = function() {
        if (ticketDescription.hasClass('invalid-textarea')) ticketDescription.removeClass('invalid-textarea');
    };
    ticketDescription.unbind('change',removeTicketDescriptionInvalidClassHandler);
    ticketDescription.on('change', removeTicketDescriptionInvalidClassHandler);*/

    var removeContactNameInvalidClassHandler = function(){inventoryNum.parent().find('.material_like').toggleClass('invalid-textarea', false);};
    inventoryNum.unbind('change',removeContactNameInvalidClassHandler);
    inventoryNum.on('change', removeContactNameInvalidClassHandler);

    var removeContactPhoneInvalidClassHandler = function(){contactPhone.toggleClass('invalid-textarea', false);};
    contactPhone.unbind('change', removeContactPhoneInvalidClassHandler);
    contactPhone.on('change', removeContactPhoneInvalidClassHandler);


    var removeFileInvalidClassHandler = function(){fileSelector.toggleClass('invalid-textarea', false);};
    fileSelector.unbind('change', removeFileInvalidClassHandler);
    fileSelector.on('change', removeFileInvalidClassHandler);

    if (themeSelector.val() == null) {
        isValid = false;
        fields.push('\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0');
        themeSelector.parent().find('.material_like').toggleClass('invalid-textarea', true);
    }
    if (isInventory && !inventoryNum.val()) {
        isValid = false;
        fields.push('\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80');
        inventoryNum.parent().find('.material_like').toggleClass('invalid-textarea', true);
    } else if (isFileRequired && (!fileIdArray || !fileIdArray.length)) {
        isValid = false;
        fields.push('\xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xBB');
        fileSelector.toggleClass('invalid-textarea', true);
    }
    if (!isValid) {
        if (fields.length > 1) {
            $messageModal.find('p').text('\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F ' + fields.join(', ') + ' \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F');
        } else {
            $messageModal.find('p').text('\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5 ' + fields[0] + ' \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F');
        }
        $messageModal.find('a').removeAttr('href');
        $messageModal.modal('open');
    }
    return isValid;
}

//\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x84\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E \xD1\x81 \xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB5\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2 description
function getResultFromField(templateFields) {
    //console.log(templateFields);
    var result = [];
    var rangeVal = "", rangeValIterator = 0;
    templateFields.each(function (index) {
        var fieldAnswer = "";
        if ($(this).hasClass('t_check')) {
            if ($(this).prop('checked') == true) {
                fieldAnswer = '\xD0\x94\xD0\xB0';
            } else {
                fieldAnswer = '\xD0\x9D\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82';
            }
        } else if ($(this).hasClass('t_data_range')) {
            if($(this).val() !== ""){
                if (rangeValIterator == 0) {
                    rangeVal += $(this).val();
                    rangeVal += "\xE2\x80\x94";
                    rangeValIterator = 1;

                } else {
                    rangeVal += $(this).val();
                    fieldAnswer = rangeVal;
                    rangeVal = "";
                    rangeValIterator = 0;
                }
            } else {
                fieldAnswer = null;
            }

        } else {
            if(typeof $(this).attr('multiple') !== typeof undefined && typeof $(this).attr('multiple') !== false) {
                fieldAnswer = [];
                $(this).find('option:selected').each(function () {
                    if(!$(this).is(':disabled')){
                        fieldAnswer.push($(this).text());
                    }
                });
                if(!fieldAnswer.length) fieldAnswer = null;
            } else {
                fieldAnswer = $(this).val();
            }

        }
        if (rangeValIterator == 0 && fieldAnswer !== null && fieldAnswer !== "") {
            var template = $(this).data("template");
            if (template) {
                if (template instanceof Object) {
                    template = "";
                } else {
                    template = "" + template;
                }
                if (template.indexOf("[]") != -1) {
                    result.push(template.replace("[]", fieldAnswer));
                } else {
                    result.push(template + " - " + fieldAnswer);
                }
            } else {
                result.push(decodeURIComponent($(this).data("name")) + " - " + fieldAnswer);
            }
        }

    });
    return result;
}

function requiredDescriptionCheck() {
    var $variableRequirement = $('#variableRequirement');
    var $requiredTemplateFields = $('.required');
    if($requiredTemplateFields.length > 0){
        $variableRequirement.empty();
        glValidator = false;
    } else {
        $variableRequirement.empty().append("*");
        glValidator = true;
    }
}

function toTranslit(text) {
    return text.replace(/([\xD0\xB0-\xD1\x8F\xD1\x91])/gi,
        function (all, ch, i) {
            var code = ch.charCodeAt(0),
                index = code == 1025 || code == 1105 ? 0 :
                    code > 1071 ? code - 1071 : code - 1039,
                t = ['yo', 'a', 'b', 'v', 'g', 'd', 'e', 'zh',
                    'z', 'i', 'y', 'k', 'l', 'm', 'n', 'o', 'p',
                    'r', 's', 't', 'u', 'f', 'h', 'c', 'ch', 'sh',
                    'shch', '', 'y', '', 'e', 'yu', 'ya'
                ];
            return t[index];
        })
}

//\xD0\x9A\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD1\x83\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80. \xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE URL /#catalog.
function catalog(template) {
    initShop(template);
}

function initShop(template) {
    hideSideNav();

    dust.renderSource(template, {}, function (err, out) {
        var appWrapper = $('#main_wrapper');
        appWrapper.empty();
        appWrapper.append(template);

        var router = $.Router();
        var query = router.args ? router.args["search"] ? router.args["search"] : "" : "";
        if (!query) {
            var currentLevel = router.path[1] ? router.path[1] : 0;
            if (window.outerWidth > 400) {
                //renderBreadcrumbs(currentLevel, router);
            }
            $.ajax({
                type: 'GET',
                url: 'api/user/catalog/node/' + currentLevel + '/children/'
            }).done(function (data) {
                if (data == "") {
                    if (currentLevel !== 0) {
                        $.ajax({
                            type: 'GET',
                            url: 'api/user/catalog/node/' + currentLevel + '/service/'
                        }).done(function (services) {
                            $.ajax({
                                type: 'GET',
                                url: 'api/user/catalog/breadcrumbs/' + currentLevel
                            }).done(function(breadcrumbs) {
                                var data = {services: services, breadcrumbs: breadcrumbs};
                                showForm(data, router);
                            });
                        })
                    }
                } else {
                    $('#catalog-wrapper').append('<div class="container">\\n' +
                        '    <div class="row">\\n' +
                        '        <div class="col s12">\\n' +
                        '            <h1 class=\\'catalog-header margins\\'>\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBC \xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB1\xD1\x83\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD1\x89\xD1\x8C?</h1>\\n' +
                        '        </div>\\n' +
                        '        <div class="col l2 m3 s12">\\n' +
                        '            <div style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px">\\n' +
                        '                <strong class="ee-st-label">\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x88\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F</strong>\\n' +
                        '            </div>\\n' +
                        '        </div>\\n' +
                        '        <div class="col l10 m9 s12" id="ticketNameBlock">\\n' +
                        '            <div class="input-field" style="margin: 0;">\\n' +
                        '                <select class="browser-default required" id="placeFor">\\n' +
                        '                </select>\\n' +
                        '            </div>\\n' +
                        '        </div>\\n' +
                        '    </div>\\n' +
                        '</div>');

                    $('#bread_wrapper').html('<a href=\\'/#\\' class=\\'header-logo\\'><img src=\\'../../images/logo-5ka.png\\'></a><span>\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0</span>');

                    var $placeFor = $('#placeFor');
                    $placeFor.select2({
                        containerCssClass: 'material_like',
                        placeholder: "\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5",
                        ajax: {
                            url: "/api/shops",
                            dataType: 'json',
                            type: "GET",
                            data: function (params) {
                                return {
                                    q : params.term ? params.term : "",
                                    page : (params.page || 1) - 1
                                };
                            },
                            processResults: function (data, params) {
                                return {
                                    results : data.content,
                                    pagination : {
                                        more: !data.last
                                    }
                                };
                            }
                        },
                        escapeMarkup: function (markup) { return markup; }, // let our custom formatter work
                        templateResult: function (group) {
                            return group.location;
                        },
                        templateSelection: function (group) {
                            return group.location ? group.location : group.text;
                        },
                        width: "100%"
                    });

                    $placeFor.on('change', function () {
                        var self = $(this);
                        loadCatalog($(this).val(), $placeFor.select2('data').find(function(next){return next.id === self.val()}).location);
                    });
                }
            })
        } else {
            if (router.args.shopid && router.args.shopname) {
                loadCatalog(router.args.shopid, router.args.shopname, query);
            } else {
                location.hash = "catalog";
            }
        }
    });
}

//\xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD1\x83\xD1\x87\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xB1\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B \xD1\x81\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82 ID \xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD1\x8D\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0
function loadCatalog(shopId, shopName, query) {
    //debugger;
    var router = $.Router();
    if (query) {
        $.ajax({
            type: 'GET',
            url: 'api/user/catalog/search?q=' + query  + "&shopid=" + shopId
        }).done(function (data) {
            showLevel(data.nodes, decodeURIComponent(query), router, data.services, shopId, shopName);
        });
    } else {

        var currentLevel = router.path[1] ? router.path[1] : 0;
        if (window.outerWidth > 400) {
            //renderBreadcrumbs(currentLevel, router);
        }
        $.ajax({
            type: 'GET',
            url: 'api/user/catalog/node/' + currentLevel + '/children/'
        }).done(function (data) {
            if (data == "") {
                if (currentLevel !== 0) {
                    $.ajax({
                        type: 'GET',
                        url: 'api/user/catalog/node/' + currentLevel + '/service/'
                    }).done(function (services) {
                        $.ajax({
                            type: 'GET',
                            url: 'api/user/catalog/breadcrumbs/' + currentLevel
                        }).done(function(breadcrumbs) {
                            var data = {services: services, breadcrumbs: breadcrumbs};
                            showForm(data, router);
                        });
                    })
                }
            } else {
                showLevel(data, undefined, router, undefined, shopId, shopName);
            }
        })
    }
}

//\xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB5
function showServices(services, query, shopId, shopName) {
    var $mainWrapper = $('#catalog-wrapper');
    if (services.length > 0) {
        var serviceList = '<div class="row"><div class="col l12 m12 s12"><p class="catalog-subtext">\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE <strong>\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBC</strong> \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2: \\"' + query + '\\"</p></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col l12 m12 s12"><ul class="collection">';
        services.forEach(function (service) {
            serviceList += '<li data-id="' + service.id + '" data-parent="' + service.parentId + '" class="collection-item search-service-li">' + service.parentName + ' -> ' + service.name + '</li>';
        });
        serviceList += '</ul></div></div>';

        $mainWrapper.children("div").append(serviceList);

        var $searchService = $('.search-service-li');
        $searchService.unbind('click');
        $searchService.on('click', function () {
            var parentId = $(this).data('parent');
            var serviceId = $(this).data('id');
            location.href = '/#catalog/' + parentId + '?service=' + serviceId + '&shopid=' + shopId + '&shopname=' + encodeURI(shopName);
        });
    } else {
        $mainWrapper.children("div").append('<div class="row"><div class="col l12 m12 s12"><p class="catalog-subtext">\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x83 "' + query + '" \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB9\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE. \xD0\x92\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD0\xB7\xD1\x83\xD0\xB9\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC.</p></div></div>');
    }
}

//\xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x81\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x8D\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5
function showLevel(data, query, router, serviceQuery, shopId, shopName) {
    $.ajax({
        type: "GET",
        url: "api/user/catalog/treeview?shopid=" + shopId
    }).done(function (data) {
        // \xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x8A\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x81\xD1\x81\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x83 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB0
        var serviceLinks = [];
        //\xD0\xA7\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB2\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80
        var $mainWrapper = $("#catalog-wrapper");
        $mainWrapper.empty();

        //\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x81 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC
        $mainWrapper.append("<div class='container' style='margin-top: 30px;'>");
        $mainWrapper.children("div").append("<div class='row'>" +
            "<div class='col l12 m12 s12'>" +
            "<h1 class='catalog-header margins'>\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBC \xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB1\xD1\x83\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD1\x89\xD1\x8C?</h1>" +
            "<p class='catalog-subtext'>\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5</p>" +
            "</div>" +
            "<div class='col l12 m12 s12'>" +
            "<div class='catalog-search-wrapper search-wrapper'><input class='PL_10_BS_BB' id='search' placeholder='\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBC' value ='" + (query ? query : "") + "'><i id='search_button' class='material-icons'>search</i><i id='clear_search' class='" + (query ? "" : "ee-hidden ") + "search-clear material-icons'>close</i></div></div>");


        var nestedAccordion = "";

        if (data !== []) {
            drawAccordionLevel(data);
        }

        //\xD0\xAF <3 \xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83\xD1\x80\xD1\x81\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B, \xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8E\xD1\x82 \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B
        function drawAccordionLevel(data) {
            nestedAccordion += '<ul class="collapsible catalog-ul" data-collapsible="expandable">';
            data.forEach(function (node) {
                nestedAccordion += '<li><div data-id="' + node.id + '" class="collapsible-header">' + node.name + '</div><div class="catalog-collapsible collapsible-body">';
                if (node.hasOwnProperty("children")) {
                    drawAccordionLevel(node.children);
                } else if (node.hasOwnProperty("services")) {
                    nestedAccordion += '<ul class="nested-services">';
                    node.services.forEach(function (service) {
                        serviceLinks.push({name: service.name, link: '/#catalog/' + node.id + '?service=' + service.id + '&shopid=' + shopId + '&shopname=' + shopName});
                        nestedAccordion += '<li><a href="/#catalog/' + service.parentId + '?service=' + service.id  + '&shopid=' + shopId + '&shopname=' + shopName + '">' + service.name + '</a></li>';
                    });
                }
                nestedAccordion += '</div></li>';
            });
            nestedAccordion += '</ul>';
        }
        nestedAccordion += '<div class="button-left"><a href="/#tickets?state=opened" class="waves-effect waves-light btn">\xD0\x9D\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4</a></div>';
        $mainWrapper.children("div").append(nestedAccordion);

        //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBF\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2 \xD1\x82\xD0\xBE \xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD1\x83\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB8\xD1\x85 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0
        if (serviceQuery !== undefined) {
            showServices(serviceQuery, decodeURIComponent(query), shopId, shopName);
        }

        $(document).ready(function(){
            $('.collapsible').collapsible();
        });

        //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBB\xD1\x83\xD0\xBF\xD1\x83
        $('#search_button').click(function () {
            var searchText = $("#search").val();
            if (searchText !== "") {
                breadcrumbs = [];
                location.href = "#catalog?search=" + encodeURIComponent(searchText) + ((router.args["user"]) ? ("&user=" + router.args["user"]) : ("")) + "&shopid=" + shopId + "&shopname=" + shopName;
            } else if (searchText === "") {
                breadcrumbs = [];
                location.href = "#catalog" + ((router.args["user"]) ? ("?user=" + router.args["user"]) : (""));
            }
        });

        //\xD0\x9A\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA
        var clearSearch = $('#clear_search'),
            searchInput = $("#search");

        //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE Enter
        searchInput.on('keypress', function (evt) {
            var searchText = $("#search").val();

            var key = evt.which || evt.charCode || evt.keyCode || 0;

            if ((key == 13) && (searchText != "")) {
                breadcrumbs = [];
                location.href = "#catalog?search=" + encodeURIComponent(searchText) + ((router.args["user"]) ? ("&user=" + router.args["user"]) : ("")) + "&shopid=" + shopId + "&shopname=" + shopName;
            } else if ((key == 13) && (searchText == "")) {
                breadcrumbs = [];
                location.href = "#catalog" + ((router.args["user"]) ? ("?user=" + router.args["user"]) : (""));
            }
        });

        // \xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
        var autocomplete;

        var names = {};
        serviceLinks.forEach(function (value) {
            names[value.name] = null;
        });
        searchInput.autocomplete({
            data: names,
            onAutocomplete: function (val) {
                serviceLinks.forEach(function (value) {
                    if(val === value.name) {
                        location.href = value.link;
                        return;
                    }
                })
            }
        });

        //\xD0\xA7\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA
        clearSearch.on('click', function (e) {
            searchInput.val("");
            if (!clearSearch.hasClass("ee-hidden")) clearSearch.addClass("ee-hidden");
            breadcrumbs = [];
            location.href = "#catalog" + ((router.args["user"]) ? ("?user=" + router.args["user"]) : (""));
        });

        //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD1\x8F\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC
        searchInput.on('input', function () {
            if (searchInput.val() !== "") {
                if (clearSearch.hasClass("ee-hidden")) clearSearch.removeClass("ee-hidden");
            } else {
                if (!clearSearch.hasClass("ee-hidden")) clearSearch.addClass("ee-hidden");
            }
        })
    });
}

//\xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
function showForm(data, router) {
    var shopId = router.args.shopid;
    var shopName = router.args.shopname;
    if (!shopId || !shopName) location.hash = "catalog";
    if(router.args.user){
        $.ajax({
            type: "GET",
            url: "api/user/" + router.args.user + "/info"
        }).done(function (userInfo) {
            drawForm(userInfo);
        })
    } else {
        drawForm(undefined);
    }
    function drawForm(userInfo) {
        var serviceId;
        var isInventory = false;
        var rootServiceId;
        var serviceIdCandidate;
        var questionResult = [];
        $.ajax({
            url: 'engineer/addticket.dust',
            contentType: "charset=utf-8"
        }).done(function (template) {
            if (userInfo !== undefined){
                data.otherFullName = userInfo.fullName;
            }
            data.shopname = decodeURI(shopName);
            dust.renderSource(template, data, function (err, out) {
                var $mainWrapper = $("#catalog-wrapper");
                $('')
                $mainWrapper.empty();
                $mainWrapper.append(out);
                var addTicketPath = window.location.hash;
                window.scrollTo(0, 0);

                        //restoreDraft(cookieDraft, router);

                    })
                }*/

                //\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x83\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F

            function reloadInventoryNumber () {
                if (serviceId)
                $.ajax({
                    url: "/api/inventoryNumbers?serviceId=" + serviceId + "&shopId=" + shopId,
                    dataType: 'json',
                    type: "GET"
                }).done(function(data) {
                    //\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x83, \xD1\x82\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD1\x8F\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 \xD1\x81 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC
                    if (data.content && data.content.length > 0) {
                        $inventoryNum.val(null);
                        $inventoryNum.empty();
                        $inventoryNum.select2({
                            containerCssClass: 'material_like',
                            placeholder: "\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80",
                            disabled: false,
                            ajax: {
                                url: "api/inventoryNumbers?shopId=" + shopId + "&serviceId=" + serviceId,
                                dataType: 'json',
                                type: "GET",
                                data: function (params) {
                                    return {
                                        serviceId: serviceId,
                                        q: params.term ? params.term : "",
                                        page: (params.page || 1) - 1
                                    };
                                },
                                processResults: function (data, params) {
                                    return {
                                        results: data.content,
                                        pagination: {
                                            more: !data.last
                                        }
                                    };
                                }
                            },
                            escapeMarkup: function (markup) {
                                return markup;
                            }, // let our custom formatter work
                            templateResult: function (group) {
                                return group.number + " \xE2\x80\x94 " + group.name;
                            },
                            templateSelection: function (group) {
                                return group.number ? group.number + " \xE2\x80\x94 " + group.name : group.text;
                            },
                            language: {
                                noResults: function (params) {
                                    return "\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2";
                                }
                            },
                            width: "100%"
                        });
                    } else {
                        $inventoryNum.select2({
                            containerCssClass: 'material_like',
                            placeholder: "\xD0\x98\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB2\xD1\x83\xD1\x8E\xD1\x82",
                            disabled: true,
                            width: "100%"
                        });
                    }

                })
            }

            var templateWrapper = $('#service_template');
            problemSelector.unbind('change');
            problemSelector.on('change', function () {
                //checkInventary($(this).val());
                //checkDuplicates($(this).val()); TODO: \xD0\x9F\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 \xD0\xB4\xD1\x83\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4 \xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81-\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x86\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x81 \xD0\xA2\xD0\xA15
                //saveDraftToObject(router);

                $('.ajax-upload-dragdrop').removeClass('red-dotted-border');

                if (templateWrapper.hasClass('template-ext')) {
                    templateWrapper.removeClass('template-ext')
                }

                templateWrapper.empty();
                serviceId = $(this).val();
                rootServiceId = $(this).val();

                if ($inventoryNum.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible")) {
                    $inventoryNum.val(null);
                    $inventoryNum.select2('destroy');
                    //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD1\x89\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C, \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBD\xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8E\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x88\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7 options \xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD1\x85 \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xC2\xAF\\(o_o)/\xC2\xAF
                    $inventoryNum.empty();
                }

                for (var i = 0; i < data.services.length; i++) {
                    if ($(this).val() == data.services[i].id) {
                        var alertMessage = $('#ticket_alert');
                        //\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x8F\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9, \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x81\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB6
                        if (data.services[i].danger) {
                            if (alertMessage.hasClass('ee-hidden')) alertMessage.removeClass('ee-hidden');
                        } else {
                            if (!alertMessage.hasClass('ee-hidden')) alertMessage.addClass('ee-hidden');
                        }
                        //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x83 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C \xD1\x88\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD, \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E
                        if (data.services[i].template != undefined) {

                            templateWrapper.append("<div class='row'><div class='col l12 m12 s12'><strong class='ee-st-label'>\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD1\x83\xD0\xB9\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0, \xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD1\x87\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x84\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E</strong></div></div>");
                            if (!templateWrapper.hasClass('template-ext')) {
                                templateWrapper.addClass('template-ext')
                            }
                            initTemplateLevel(templateWrapper, data.services[i].template, data.services[i].template);
                        }
                        //renderArticles(serviceId);
                        requiredDescriptionCheck();
                    }
                }

                serviceId = $(this).val();
                reloadInventoryNumber();
            });

            problemSelector.val(null).select2({
                containerCssClass: 'material_like',
                width: "100%",
                minimumResultsForSearch: Infinity,
                placeholder: '\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBF \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B'
            });

            //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x81 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC
            if (router.args){
                problemSelector.val(router.args['service']);
                //problemSelector.material_select();
                problemSelector.trigger('change');
            }

            /*//\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB4\xD1\x83\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B
            function checkDuplicates(id) {
                if (id) {
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "GET",
                        url: "api/service/" + id + "/tickets/?state=0,1,2,3"
                    }).done(function (duplicates) {
                        var $duplicateAlert = $("#duplicateAlert");
                        if (duplicates.numberOfElements > 0) {
                            if ($duplicateAlert.hasClass("ee-hidden")){$duplicateAlert.removeClass("ee-hidden")}
                        } else {
                            if (!$duplicateAlert.hasClass("ee-hidden")){$duplicateAlert.addClass("ee-hidden")}
                        }
                    });
                }
            }*/
