// \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
function restoreFilters() {
    if (!~previuosUrl.indexOf('tasks') && !~previuosUrl.indexOf('tickets')){
        var filterSetting = $.cookie('filterSetting') ? JSON.parse($.cookie('filterSetting')) : null;
        if (filterSetting) {
            if (location.href !== filterSetting.page) {
                location.href = filterSetting.page;
                currentUrl = '';
            } else {
                $('#dateStart').val(filterSetting.dateStart).trigger('change');
                $('#dateEnd').val(filterSetting.dateEnd).trigger('change');
                $('#overdue').prop('checked', filterSetting.overdue);
                for (var filterName in filterSetting.filters) {
                    if (filterSetting.filters.hasOwnProperty(filterName)) {
                        if (!filterSetting.filters[filterName]) {
                            $('label[for="' + filterName + '"]').trigger('click');
                        }
                    }
                }
                $('#smhoSelect').val(filterSetting.smho).trigger('change');
                // \xD0\x92\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x89\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F
                if (filterSetting.cat1) {
                    var $cat1 = $('#catlvl1');
                    $cat1.empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.cat1.value + '">'
                        + filterSetting.cat1.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.cat1.value)
                    if (filterSetting.cat1.services) {
                        $cat1.trigger({
                            type: 'select2:select',
                            params: {
                                data: filterSetting.cat1
                            }
                        });
                        initTheme(filterSetting.cat1.services);
                    } else {
                        $cat1.trigger('change');
                    }
                    if (filterSetting.cat2) {
                        var $cat2 = $('#catlvl2');
                        $cat2.empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.cat2.value + '">'
                            + filterSetting.cat2.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.cat2.value);
                        if (filterSetting.cat2.services) {
                            $cat2.trigger({
                                type: 'select2:select',
                                params: {
                                    data: filterSetting.cat2
                                }
                            });
                            initTheme(filterSetting.cat2.services);
                        } else {
                            $cat2.trigger('change');
                        }
                        if (filterSetting.cat3) {
                            var $cat3 = $('#catlvl3');
                            $cat3.empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.cat3.value + '">'
                                + filterSetting.cat3.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.cat3.value);
                            if (filterSetting.cat3.services) {
                                $cat3.trigger({
                                    type: 'select2:select',
                                    params: {
                                        data: filterSetting.cat3
                                    }
                                });
                                initTheme(filterSetting.cat3.services);
                            } else {
                                $cat3.trigger('change');
                            }
                            if (filterSetting.cat4) {
                                var $cat4 = $('#catlvl4');
                                $cat4.empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.cat4.value + '">'
                                    + filterSetting.cat4.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.cat4.value);
                                if (filterSetting.cat4.services) {
                                    $cat4.trigger({
                                        type: 'select2:select',
                                        params: {
                                            data: filterSetting.cat4
                                        }
                                    });
                                    initTheme(filterSetting.cat4.services);
                                } else {
                                    $cat4.trigger('change');
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    function initTheme (services) {
                        var theme = $('#theme');
                        theme.parent().show();
                        if (theme.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible")) {
                            theme.select2('destroy');
                        }
                        theme.select2({
                            containerCssClass: 'select-wrapper margins',
                            placeholder: "\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x83",
                            data: services,
                            allowClear: true,
                            minimumResultsForSearch: 'infinity',
                            escapeMarkup: function (markup) {
                                return markup;
                            }, // let our custom formatter work
                            templateResult: function (group) {
                                return group.name;
                            },
                            templateSelection: function (group) {
                                return group.name ? group.name : group.text;
                            },
                            width: "100%"
                        });
                        theme.val(filterSetting.theme ? filterSetting.theme.value : null).trigger('change');
                    }

                }
                if (filterSetting.engineer) {
                    $('#engineerSelect').empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.engineer.value + '">'
                        + filterSetting.engineer.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.engineer.value).trigger('change');
                }
                if (filterSetting.location) {
                    $('#locationSelect').empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.location.value + '">'
                        + filterSetting.location.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.location.value).trigger('change');
                }
                if (filterSetting.division) {
                    $('#divisionSelect').empty().append('<option value="' + filterSetting.division.value + '">'
                        + filterSetting.division.text  + '</option>').val(filterSetting.division.value).trigger('change');
                }
                if (Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0) > 992) {
                    if (filterSetting.hideSideNav) {
                        $hideNavBar.trigger('click');
                    } else {
                        $showNavBar.trigger('click');
                    }
                }
                return true;
            }
        }
    }
}

// \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD1\x85\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
function saveFilters( url ){
    if ($('ul.pagination li.active').length > 0) {
        var filters = $('#nav-mobile').find('.card-panel.switch:not(.hide)');
        var $cat1 = $('#catlvl1'), $cat2 = $('#catlvl2'), $cat3 = $('#catlvl3'), $cat4 = $('#catlvl4'), $theme = $('#theme'),
            $engineer = $('#engineerSelect'), $location = $('#locationSelect'), $division = $('#divisionSelect');
        $cat1 = $cat1.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $cat1.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $cat2 = $cat2.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $cat2.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $cat3 = $cat3.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $cat3.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $cat4 = $cat4.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $cat4.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $theme = $theme.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $theme.select2('data')[0] : null;

        $engineer = $engineer.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $engineer.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $location = $location.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $location.select2('data')[0] : null;
        $division = $division.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible") ? $division.select2('data')[0] : null;
        var filterSetting = {
            page: url ? url : location.href,
            smho: $('#smhoSelect').val(),
            dateStart: $('#dateStart').val(),
            dateEnd: $('#dateEnd').val(),
            cat1: $cat1 ? {
                value: $cat1.id,
                text: $cat1.name ? $cat1.name : $cat1.text,
                services: $cat1.services
            } : null,
            cat2: $cat2 ? {
                value: $cat2.id,
                text: $cat2.name,
                services: $cat2.services
            } : null,
            cat3: $cat3 ? {
                value: $cat3.id,
                text: $cat3.name,
                services: $cat3.services
            } : null,
            cat4: $cat4 ? {
                value: $cat4.id,
                text: $cat4.name,
                services: $cat4.services
            } : null,
            theme: $theme ? {
                value: $theme.id,
                text: $theme.name
            } : null,
            engineer: $engineer ? {
                value: $engineer.id,
                name: $engineer.text
            } : null,
            location: $location ? {
                value: $location.id,
                name: $location.text
            } : null,
            division: $division ? {
                value: $division.id,
                name: $division.text
            } : null,
            overdue: $('#overdue').prop('checked'),
            filters: {}
        };
        if (!~filterSetting.page.indexOf('page')) {
            filterSetting.page += "&page=" + $('ul.pagination li.active').data('page');
        } else {
            filterSetting.page = filterSetting.page.slice(0, filterSetting.page.indexOf('page') - 1) + "&page=" + $('ul.pagination li.active').data('page');
        }
        filters.each(function (index, element) {
            filterSetting.filters[$(element).parent().attr('for')] = $(element).find('input[type="checkbox"]').prop('checked');
        });
        if (Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0) > 992 && $sidenav.css('display') === 'none') {
            filterSetting.hideSideNav = true;
        }
        $.cookie('filterSetting', JSON.stringify(filterSetting));
    }
}

function showSideNav() {
    if (Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0) <= 992) {
        $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', false);
        $sidenav.sideNav('hide');
        $sidenav.show();
    } else {
        if ($sidenav.css('display') === 'none') {
            $showNavBar.show();
        } else {
            $hideNavBar.show();
        }
    }
    $('a.button-collapse.hamburger').show(0);
    isHiddenNav = false;
}

function hideSideNav() {
    $('#nav-mobile').sideNav('hide');
    $sidenav.hide();
    $showNavBar.hide();
    $hideNavBar.hide();
    $('a.button-collapse.hamburger').hide(0);
    $headerFooterMain.css('padding-left', '0');
    isHiddenNav = true;
}

function wrapper(template, user, rights){
    var mainContainerData = {};
    mainContainerData['fullName'] = user.fullName;
    mainContainerData['role'] = roleToName(role);

    $.ajax({
        type: 'GET',
        url: 'api/ticket/countByState/4'
    }).done(function (unreadTicketsCount) {
        var unreadCount = unreadTicketsCount && unreadTicketsCount.count ? unreadTicketsCount.count : 0;
        renderMain(unreadCount);
    }).fail(function () {
        renderMain(0);
    });

    function renderMain(unreadTicketsCount) {
        if (unreadTicketsCount > 0) {
            mainContainerData["unreadCount"] = unreadTicketsCount;
            /*if (router.path[0] != "main") {
                mainContainerData.unreadState = true;
            }*/
        }
        //\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB3\xD1\x80\xD1\x83\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x84\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E \xD0\xBE \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7 Cookie
        mainContainerData.actions = rights.actions;
        mainContainerData.roles = rights.roles;
        mainContainerData.companyId = $.cookie("currentCompany");

        var menuState = getMenuStateFromJson();
        for(var menuName in menuState) {
            if (menuState[menuName] === 'opened') {
                mainContainerData[menuName] = "display: block";
                mainContainerData[menuName + "sign"] = "remove";
            } else {
                mainContainerData[menuName] = "";
                mainContainerData[menuName + "sign"] = "add";
            }
        }

        switch (role){
            case 'master': mainContainerData.icon = 'star'; break;
            case 'leader': mainContainerData.icon = 'supervisor_account'; break;
            case 'senior': mainContainerData.icon = 'person'; break;
        }
        dust.renderSource(template, mainContainerData, function (err, out) {
            var $bodyWrapper = $('#app');
            $bodyWrapper.empty();
            $bodyWrapper.append(out);

            $sidenav = $('#nav-mobile');
            $hideNavBar = $('#hideNavBar');
            $showNavBar = $('#showNavBar');

            //\xD0\x9D\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x8D\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B \xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD1\x87\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8

            //\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8E\xD1\x89\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB \xD1\x81 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD1\x81\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
            $('#m_version').on('click', function () {
                versionControl();
            });

            $headerFooterMain = $('header, footer, main');

            //\xD0\x98\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB3\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 SideNav (\xD0\x91\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8E)
            var prevWidth = Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0);
            if (prevWidth > 992) {
                $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', true);
            } else {
                $hideNavBar.hide();
                $showNavBar.hide();
            }
            $(window).resize(function () {
                var currentWidth = Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0);
                if (prevWidth <= 992 && currentWidth > 992 && !isHiddenNav){
                    $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', true);
                    $showNavBar.trigger('click');
                } else if (prevWidth > 992 && currentWidth <= 992 && !isHiddenNav) {
                    $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', false);
                    $hideNavBar.hide();
                    $showNavBar.hide();
                    $sidenav.show();
                    $sidenav.sideNav('hide');
                    $headerFooterMain.css('padding-left', '');
                }
                prevWidth = currentWidth;
            });
            $(".button-collapse").sideNav({
                onOpen: function(){
                    $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', true);
                    if (Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0) >= 992) {
                        $hideNavBar.show();
                    }
                },
                onClose: function(){
                    if (Math.max(document.documentElement.clientWidth, window.innerWidth || 0) < 992) {
                        $sidenav.toggleClass('crutch', false);
                    }
                }
            });


            $hideNavBar.on('click', function () {
                $sidenav.hide();
                $('main, footer, header').css('padding-left', '0');
                $hideNavBar.hide();
                $showNavBar.show()
            });

            $showNavBar.on('click', function () {
                $sidenav.show();
                $('main, footer, header').css('padding-left', '300px');
                $hideNavBar.show();
                $showNavBar.hide();
            });

            var $eeMenu = $('.ee-menu-card');

            //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD1\x8F\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8E
            $('#ee-menu-button').on('click', function (e) {
                e.stopPropagation();
                $eeMenu.toggleClass('ee-hidden');
            });

            $('body').on('click', function () {
                if (!$eeMenu.hasClass('ee-hidden')){$eeMenu.addClass('ee-hidden')}
            });

            //\xD0\x98\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0
            $('#m_logout').on('click', function (e) {
                e.stopPropagation();
                $.ajax({
                    type: 'GET',
                    url: 'api/logout',
                    success: function () {
                        $.cookie('sessionExpired', false);
                        window.location = '/login';
                    }
                });
            });

            //\xD0\x9A\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8E
            var collapsibleMenu = $('.collapsible-header');
            collapsibleMenu.each(function () {
                if (!$(this).find('i.collapce-icon').text()) {
                    $(this).find('i.collapce-icon').text('add')
                }
            });

            collapsibleMenu.on('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                var menuOption = $(this);
                var menuState = getMenuStateFromJson();
                if (menuOption.nextAll('div').css('display') == 'none') {
                    menuOption.find('i.collapce-icon').text('remove');
                    menuOption.nextAll('div').css('display', 'block');
                    menuState[menuOption.data('linkname')] = 'opened';
                } else {
                    menuOption.find('i.collapce-icon').text('add');
                    menuOption.nextAll('div').css('display', 'none');
                    menuState[menuOption.data('linkname')] = 'collapsed';
                }
                $.cookie(menuStateCookiesName, JSON.stringify(menuState));
            });

            var $breadWrapper = $('#bread_wrapper');
            $breadWrapper.empty();

            //\xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
            $sidenav.find('.collapsible').collapsible({
                onOpen: function(el) { $sidenav.find('.collapsible-header .badge i').toggleClass('open', true); }, // Callback for Collapsible open
                onClose: function(el) { $sidenav.find('.collapsible-header .badge i').toggleClass('open', false); } // Callback for Collapsible close
            });

            //\xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x86\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x84\xD1\x80 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8E\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x87\xD0\xB0
            $sidenav.find('.switch input[type="checkbox"]').on('change', function(){
                if (!$(this).prop('checked') && $sidenav.find('.card-panel.switch:not(.inactive):not(.hide)').length <= 1)
                        $(this).prop('checked', true);
                else $(this).closest('.card-panel').toggleClass('inactive');
            });

            $sidenav.find('.datepicker').pickadate({

                // \xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB4\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x81\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x83\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB8
                onOpen: function () {

            (function categoriesSelect2() {
                var catlvl1 = $('#catlvl1'),
                    catlvl2 = $('#catlvl2'),
                    catlvl3 = $('#catlvl3'),
                    catlvl4 = $('#catlvl4'),
                    theme = $('#theme'),
                    ajaxData = [];
                var getSelect2Object = function(url, classes) {
                    return {
                        containerCssClass: 'select-wrapper ' + (classes ? classes : ''),
                        placeholder: "\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8E",
                        ajax: {
                            url: url,
                            dataType: 'json',
                            type: "GET",
                            data: function (params) {
                                return {
                                    q: params.term ? params.term : "",
                                    page: (params.page || 1) - 1
                                };
                            },
                            processResults: function (data, params) {
                                data.content.forEach(function (el) {
                                    ajaxData.push(el);
                                });
                                return {
                                    results: data.content,
                                    pagination: {
                                        more: !data.last
                                    }
                                };
                            }
                        },
                        allowClear: true,
                        escapeMarkup: function (markup) {
                            return markup;
                        }, // let our custom formatter work
                        templateResult: function (group) {
                            return group.name;
                        },
                        templateSelection: function (group) {
                            return group.name ? group.name : group.text;
                        },
                        language: {
                            noResults: function (params) {
                                return "\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB \xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB7\xD1\x83\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2";
                            }
                        },
                        width: "100%"
                    };
                };

                catlvl2.parent().hide(0);
                catlvl3.parent().hide(0);
                catlvl4.parent().hide(0);
                theme.parent().hide(0);

                catlvl1.select2(getSelect2Object("api/user/catalog/node/0/children/pageable"));

                initCat(catlvl1, catlvl2);
                initCat(catlvl2, catlvl3);
                initCat(catlvl3, catlvl4);
                initCat(catlvl4, theme);

                // \xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8 n+1 \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x83\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8
                function initCat(parentCat, childCat){
                    parentCat.find('option:not([value="' + parentCat.val() + '"])').remove();
                    parentCat.on("change", function () {
                        theme.val(null);
                        childCat.val(null).trigger('change');
                        if (!parentCat.val()) {
                            childCat.parent().hide(0);
                            theme.parent().hide(0);
                        } else {
                            childCat.parent().show(0);
                            var services = checkServices(parentCat.val());
                            if (services) {
                                childCat.parent().hide(0);
                                initTheme(services)
                            } else {
                                theme.parent().hide(0);
                                if (childCat.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible")) {
                                    childCat.select2('destroy');
                                    //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD1\x89\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C, \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBD\xD1\x83\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8E\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x88\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7 options \xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD1\x85 \xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xC2\xAF\\(o_o)/\xC2\xAF
                                    childCat.empty();
                                }
                                childCat.select2(getSelect2Object("api/user/catalog/node/" + parentCat.val() + "/children/pageable", 'margins'));
                            }
                        }
                    });
                }

                function checkServices(id){
                    if (ajaxData) {
                        return ajaxData.find(function(el){
                            if (el.id === +id) {
                                return el.services;
                            }
                        });
                    }
                    return false;
                }

                function initTheme(services){
                    theme.parent().show();
                    if (theme.hasClass("select2-hidden-accessible")) {
                        theme.select2('destroy');
                    }
                    theme.select2({
                        containerCssClass: 'select-wrapper margins',
                        placeholder: "\xD0\x92\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x83",
                        data: services.services,
                        allowClear: true,
                        minimumResultsForSearch: 'infinity',
                        escapeMarkup: function (markup) {
                            return markup;
                        }, // let our custom formatter work
                        templateResult: function (group) {
                            return group.name;
                        },
                        templateSelection: function (group) {
                            return group.name ? group.name : group.text;
                        },
                        width: "100%"
                    });
                    theme.val(null).trigger('change');
                }
            })();

            // \xD0\xA1\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9
            var postBtn = $('.type button');
            postBtn.on('click', function(){
                var stateId = $(this).attr('data-type');
                location.hash = "#" + stateId + "?state=opened";
            });

            loadContent();
        });
    }
}
function getMenuStateFromJson() {
    var menuStateString = $.cookie(menuStateCookiesName);
    if (menuStateString && menuStateString == 'null') {
        $.removeCookie(menuStateCookiesName);
        return {};
    }
    if (menuStateString) {
        try {
            return JSON.parse(menuStateString);
        }catch (e) {
            $.removeCookie(menuStateCookiesName);
            return {};
        }
    } else {
        $.removeCookie(menuStateCookiesName);
        return {};
    }
}
//\xD0\xA4\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F, \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8E\xD1\x89\xD0\xB0\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBC\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBB \xD1\x81 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83\xD1\x89\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80\xD1\x81\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB9 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
function versionControl() {
    $.ajax({
        url: 'api/appInfo',
        type: 'GET'
    }).done(function (versionData) {
        var $versionModal = $('#version_modal');
        $versionModal.children('div').empty();
        $versionModal.children('div').append("<h5>" + versionData.name + "</h5><hr><p>" + versionData.version + "</p><p>" + versionData.buildTimestamp + "</p>");
        $versionModal.modal('open');
    });
}

function tickets(template) {
    $('label[for=appointedCheckbox] span.name').html('\xD0\x9D\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD');
    $('label[for=resolvedCheckbox] .name').html('\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD');
    $('label[for=closedCheckbox] .name').html('\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82');
    $('label[for=canceledCheckbox] .name').html('\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD');
    $('#nav-mobile h6.state-title').html('\xD0\xA1\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x83\xD1\x81 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0');
    var postsBtn = $('.type button');
    postsBtn.removeAttr('disabled');
    postsBtn.filter('[data-type=tickets]').attr('disabled', 'true');
    dust.renderSource(template, {}, function (err, out) {
        var $mainWrapper = $("#main_wrapper");
        $mainWrapper.empty();
        $mainWrapper.append(template);

        //\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8E (\xD1\x83\xD0\xB1\xD0\xB8\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2 catalog.js)
        showSideNav();
        var router = $.Router();
        //\xD0\xA3\xD0\xBF\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBF\xD1\x83\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8E
        var menuActiveItems = $('.menu-item-active'),
            $breadWrapper = $('#bread_wrapper');
        var page = router.args ? router.args['page'] ? router.args['page'] : 1 : 1;
        var state = router.args ? router.args['state'] ? router.args['state'] : "default" : "default";
        var stateArr = "";
        var currentStateArr="";
        var $filterPanel = $('#nav-mobile .collapsible');
        var isCorrectDate = true;
        var isReset;

        menuActiveItems.removeClass('menu-item-active');

        //\xD0\x9E\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x85\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD1\x85 \xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBA
        breadcrumbs = [];
        $breadWrapper.empty();

        //\xD0\x9F\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8 \xD1\x81\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD1\x81 \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
        $filterPanel.find('.switch input[type=checkbox]').prop('checked', true);
        $filterPanel.find('.switch.card-panel').toggleClass('inactive', false);
        $filterPanel.find('.alert').removeClass('alert');
        $filterPanel.find('input[type=text]').val('');
        $filterPanel.find('#themeSelect').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#overdue').prop('checked', false);
        $filterPanel.find('label > div').toggleClass('hide', false);
        $filterPanel.find('label[for=controlCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', false);
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl1').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl2').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl3').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl4').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#theme').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#smhoSelect').val(null).trigger('change');

        isReset = restoreFilters();

        //\xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B
        $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').unbind('change');
        $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').on('change', function(){
            var $startDate = $('#dateStart');
            var $endDate = $('#dateEnd');
            if ($startDate.val() && $endDate.val()) {
                isCorrectDate = Date.parse(
                    $startDate.val().split('.').reverse().join('-')) <=
                    Date.parse($endDate.val().split('.').reverse().join('-'));
                $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').toggleClass('alert', !isCorrectDate);

            }
        });

        //\xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
        var $commitTicketsFilter = $('#commit-tickets-filter');
        $commitTicketsFilter.unbind('click');
        $commitTicketsFilter.on('click', function(){
            var query = '';
            var filters = [];
            $filterPanel.find('.card-panel:not(.inactive):not(.hide) input[data-filter]').each(function(){
                filters.push($(this).attr('data-filter'));
            });
            query = filters.length > 0 ? '?state=' + filters.join(',') : stateArr;
            for (var i=1; i<5; i++) {
                var option = $filterPanel.find('#catlvl' + i).val();
                query += option ? '&cat' + i + '=' + option : '';
            }
            var service = $('#theme').val();
            query += service ? '&service=' + service : '';
            var dateStart = $filterPanel.find('#dateStart').val();
            dateStart = dateStart ? Date.parse(dateStart.split('.').reverse().join('-')) : '';
            var dateFinish = $filterPanel.find('#dateEnd').val();
            dateFinish = dateFinish ? Date.parse(dateFinish.split('.').reverse().join('-')) : '';
            if (isCorrectDate && (dateStart || dateFinish)) {
                if(dateStart){
                    query += '&dateStart=' + dateStart;
                }
                if(dateFinish) {
                    query += '&dateFinish=' + dateFinish;
                }
            }
            var isOnlyoVerdue = $filterPanel.find('#overdue').prop('checked');
            query += isOnlyoVerdue ? '&expired=' + isOnlyoVerdue : '';
            var engineer = $('#engineerSelect').val(),
                shop = $('#locationSelect').val(),
                division = $('#divisionSelect').val(),
                smho = $('#smhoSelect').val();
            query += engineer ? '&engineer=' + engineer : '';
            query += shop ? '&shop=' + shop : '';
            query += division ? '&division=' + division : '';
            if (smho === '0') {
                query += '&withoutSmho=true';
            } else {
                query += smho ? '&smhoClassIn=' + smho : '';
            }            saveFilters();
            renderTable(query, page);
        });

        switch (state) {
            /*case "archive":
                stateArr = "?state=5&scope=my";
                var ticketsArchived = $('#tickets_archived');
                if (!ticketsArchived.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsArchived.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?archive' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;
            case "new":
                stateArr = "?state=0&scope=my";
                var ticketsPaused = $('#tickets_new');
                if (!ticketsPaused.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsPaused.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?archive' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9D\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;*/
            case "opened":
                stateArr = "?state=-1,0,1,5";
                $('#tickets_assigned').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");
                setCount();
                $filterPanel.find('label[for=resolvedCheckbox] > div, label[for=closedCheckbox] > div, label[for=canceledCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', true);
                break;
            /*case "cancelled":
                stateArr = "?state=6&scope=my";
                var ticketsCancelled = $('#tickets_cancelled');
                if (!ticketsCancelled.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsCancelled.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?canceled' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;
            case "solved":
                stateArr = "?state=4&scope=my";
                var ticketsEnded = $('#tickets_solved');
                if (!ticketsEnded.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsEnded.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?end' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;*/
            case "archive":
                stateArr = "?state=2,3,4";
                $('#tickets_in_work').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x90\xD1\x80\xD1\x85\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2</a>");
                setCount();
                $filterPanel.find('label[for=newCheckbox] > div, label[for=appointedCheckbox] > div, label[for=performedCheckbox] > div, label[for=controlCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', true);

                break;
            case "all":
                stateArr = "?state=-1,0,1,2,3,4,5";
                $('#tickets_all').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                setCount();
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x92\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");
        }

        function setCount() {
            $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter]').html(0);
            $.ajax({
                type: 'GET',
                url: '/api/ticket/countByState/'
            }).done(function(statesInfo){
                var assigned = 0, inWork = 0, all = 0;
                // \xD0\xA1\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x81\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
                for (var i = -1; i < 5; i++){
                    $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter=' + i + ']')
                        .parent().find('b').html(0);
                }
                statesInfo.forEach(function(el){
                    $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter=' + el.stateId + ']')
                        .parent().find('b').html(el.count);
                    all += el.count;
                    switch (el.stateId) {
                        case -1:
                        case 0:
                        case 5:
                        case 1:assigned += el.count; break;
                        case 2:
                        case 3:
                        case 4: inWork += el.count; break;
                    }
                });
                $('#tickets_assigned').find('span').text(assigned);
                $('#tickets_in_work').find('span').text(inWork);
                $('#tickets_all').find('span').text(all);
            });
        }

        if (isReset) {
            $commitTicketsFilter.trigger('click');
        } else {
            renderTable(stateArr, page);
        }

        window.onhashchange = function() {
            if (!~location.hash.indexOf('tickets')) {
                window.onhashchange = loadContent;
                saveFilters(currentUrl);
            } else {
                saveFilters();
            }
            loadContent();
        };
    });
}

//\xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD1\x83 \xD1\x81 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBC \xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8
function renderTable(stateArr, page) {
    var columns = [
        {
            name: "\xE2\x84\x96 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0/\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8",
            data: "id",
            width: "16%",
            mobileView: true,
            render: function (data, row) {
                var description = '<p class=\\'small-margin\\'>';
                if (row.hasAttachments) {
                    description += "<i class=\\"material-icons inherit-font\\">attach_file</i>";
                }
                description += 'INC_' + row.id;
                if (row.taskId) {
                    description += " >> TSK_" + row.taskId;
                }

                description += "</p><p class='small-margin'><span class='state-color-badge state-color-" + row.ticketStateId + "'>" + row.ticketState + "</span>";
                if (row.taskStateId != undefined) {
                    description += "&nbsp;&gt;&gt; <span class='state-color-badge state-color-" + row.taskStateId + "'>" + row.taskState + "</span>";
                }

                description += "</p>";

        $filterPanel.find('.switch.card-panel').toggleClass('inactive', false);
        $filterPanel.find('.alert').removeClass('alert');
        $filterPanel.find('input[type=text]').val('');
        $filterPanel.find('#themeSelect').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#overdue').prop('checked', false);
        $filterPanel.find('label > div').toggleClass('hide', false);
        $filterPanel.find('label[for=controlCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', false);
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl1').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl2').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl3').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#catlvl4').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#theme').val(null).trigger('change');
        $filterPanel.find('#smhoSelect').val(null).trigger('change');

        isReset = restoreFilters();

        //\xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B
        $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').unbind('change');
        $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').on('change', function(){
            var $startDate = $('#dateStart');
            var $endDate = $('#dateEnd');
            if ($startDate.val() && $endDate.val()) {
                isCorrectDate = Date.parse(
                    $startDate.val().split('.').reverse().join('-')) <=
                    Date.parse($endDate.val().split('.').reverse().join('-'));
                $filterPanel.find('.datepicker').toggleClass('alert', !isCorrectDate);

            }
        });

        //\xD0\x9E\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2
        var $commitTicketsFilter = $('#commit-tickets-filter');
        $commitTicketsFilter.unbind('click');
        $commitTicketsFilter.on('click', function(){
            var query = '';
            var filters = [];
            $filterPanel.find('.card-panel:not(.inactive):not(.hide) input[data-filter]').each(function(){
                filters.push($(this).attr('data-filter'));
            });
            query = filters.length > 0 ? '?state=' + filters.join(',') : stateArr;
            for (var i=1; i<5; i++) {
                var option = $filterPanel.find('#catlvl' + i).val();
                query += option ? '&cat' + i + '=' + option : '';
            }
            var service = $('#theme').val();
            query += service ? '&service=' + service : '';
            var dateStart = $filterPanel.find('#dateStart').val();
            dateStart = dateStart ? Date.parse(dateStart.split('.').reverse().join('-')) : '';
            var dateFinish = $filterPanel.find('#dateEnd').val();
            dateFinish = dateFinish ? Date.parse(dateFinish.split('.').reverse().join('-')) : '';
            if (isCorrectDate && (dateStart || dateFinish)) {
                if(dateStart){
                    query += '&dateStart=' + dateStart;
                }
                if(dateFinish) {
                    query += '&dateFinish=' + dateFinish;
                }
            }
            var isOnlyoVerdue = $filterPanel.find('#overdue').prop('checked');
            query += isOnlyoVerdue ? '&expired=' + isOnlyoVerdue : '';
            var engineer = $('#engineerSelect').val(),
                shop = $('#locationSelect').val(),
                division = $('#divisionSelect').val(),
                smho = $('#smhoSelect').val();
            query += engineer ? '&engineer=' + engineer : '';
            query += shop ? '&shop=' + shop : '';
            query += division ? '&division=' + division : '';
            if (smho === '0') {
                query += '&withoutSmho=true';
            } else {
                query += smho ? '&smhoClassIn=' + smho : '';
            }            saveFilters();
            renderTable(query, page);
        });

        switch (state) {
            /*case "archive":
                stateArr = "?state=5&scope=my";
                var ticketsArchived = $('#tickets_archived');
                if (!ticketsArchived.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsArchived.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?archive' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x97\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;
            case "new":
                stateArr = "?state=0&scope=my";
                var ticketsPaused = $('#tickets_new');
                if (!ticketsPaused.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsPaused.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?archive' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9D\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;*/
            case "opened":
                stateArr = "?state=-1,0,1,5";
                $('#tickets_assigned').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBA\xD1\x80\xD1\x8B\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");
                setCount();
                $filterPanel.find('label[for=resolvedCheckbox] > div, label[for=closedCheckbox] > div, label[for=canceledCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', true);
                break;
            /*case "cancelled":
                stateArr = "?state=6&scope=my";
                var ticketsCancelled = $('#tickets_cancelled');
                if (!ticketsCancelled.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsCancelled.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?canceled' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;
            case "solved":
                stateArr = "?state=4&scope=my";
                var ticketsEnded = $('#tickets_solved');
                if (!ticketsEnded.hasClass('menu-item-active')) ticketsEnded.addClass('menu-item-active');
                $breadWrapper.append("<a href='/#tickets?end' class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");

                break;*/
            case "archive":
                stateArr = "?state=2,3,4";
                $('#tickets_in_work').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x90\xD1\x80\xD1\x85\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB2 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2</a>");
                setCount();
                $filterPanel.find('label[for=newCheckbox] > div, label[for=appointedCheckbox] > div, label[for=performedCheckbox] > div, label[for=controlCheckbox] > div').toggleClass('hide', true);

                break;
            case "all":
                stateArr = "?state=-1,0,1,2,3,4,5";
                $('#tickets_all').toggleClass('menu-item-active', true);
                setCount();
                $breadWrapper.append("<a class='breadcrumb'>\xD0\x92\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD1\x8B</a>");
        }

        function setCount() {
            $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter]').html(0);
            $.ajax({
                type: 'GET',
                url: '/api/ticket/countByState/'
            }).done(function(statesInfo){
                var assigned = 0, inWork = 0, all = 0;
                // \xD0\xA1\xD0\xB1\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x81\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB8
                for (var i = -1; i < 5; i++){
                    $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter=' + i + ']')
                        .parent().find('b').html(0);
                }
                statesInfo.forEach(function(el){
                    $filterPanel.find('input[data-filter=' + el.stateId + ']')
                        .parent().find('b').html(el.count);
                    all += el.count;
                    switch (el.stateId) {
                        case -1:
                        case 0:
                        case 5:
                        case 1:assigned += el.count; break;
                        case 2:
                        case 3:
                        case 4: inWork += el.count; break;
                    }
                });
                $('#tickets_assigned').find('span').text(assigned);
                $('#tickets_in_work').find('span').text(inWork);
                $('#tickets_all').find('span').text(all);
            });
        }

        if (isReset) {
            $commitTicketsFilter.trigger('click');
        } else {
            renderTable(stateArr, page);
        }

        window.onhashchange = function() {
            if (!~location.hash.indexOf('tickets')) {
                window.onhashchange = loadContent;
                saveFilters(currentUrl);
            } else {
                saveFilters();
            }
            loadContent();
        };
    });
}

//\xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4 \xD0\xBE\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82 \xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB1\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8\xD1\x86\xD1\x83 \xD1\x81 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBC \xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC \xD1\x84\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD1\x8C\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xB0\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB8
function renderTable(stateArr, page) {
    var columns = [
        {
            name: "\xE2\x84\x96 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0/\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8",
            data: "id",
            width: "16%",
            mobileView: true,
            render: function (data, row) {
                var description = '<p class=\\'small-margin\\'>';
                if (row.hasAttachments) {
                    description += "<i class=\\"material-icons inherit-font\\">attach_file</i>";
                }
                description += 'INC_' + row.id;
                if (row.taskId) {
                    description += " >> TSK_" + row.taskId;
                }

                description += "</p><p class='small-margin'><span class='state-color-badge state-color-" + row.ticketStateId + "'>" + row.ticketState + "</span>";
                if (row.taskStateId != undefined) {
                    description += "&nbsp;&gt;&gt; <span class='state-color-badge state-color-" + row.taskStateId + "'>" + row.taskState + "</span>";
                }

                description += "</p>";
                return description;
            }
        },
        {
            name: "\xD0\x9E\xD0\xBF\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB7\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB8",
            data: "header",
            width: "13%",
            mobileView: true,
            render: function (data, row) {
                var description = "<div class='desc_clamp'><p class='table-header-theme'>" + row.header + "</p>";
                if (row.text && row.text.trim()) {
                    description += "<p class='table-header-description'>" + row.text + "</p>";
                }
                description += "</div>";
                return description;
            }
        },
        {
            name: "\xD0\x9A\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB5\xD0\xB3\xD0\xBE\xD1\x80\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F",
            data: "category1",
            width: "13%",
            render: function (data, row) {
                var description = "";
                if (row.category1) {
                    description += "<ul class='categorisation'><li>" + row.category1;
                    if (row.category2) {
                        description += "</li><li>" + row.category2;
                        if (row.category3) {
                            description += "</li><li>" + row.category3;
                            if (row.category4) {
                                description += "</li><li>" + row.category4;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    description += "</li></ul>";
                }
                description += "</li></ul>";
                if (row.smhoClass) {
                    description += "<p class='smho  " + (row.openCommunications === 0 ? "green" : "") + "'> " +
                        "\xD0\x9A\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD1\x81\xD1\x81 \xD0\xA1\xD0\x9C\xD0\xA5\xD0\x9E: " + row.smhoClass + " (" + row.openCommunications + "/" + row.totalCommunications + ")</p>"
                }
                return description
            }
        },
        {
            name: "\xD0\x98\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB2\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x80\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB9 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80",
            data: "inventoryNumber",
            width: "11%"
        },
        {
            name: "\xD0\x9C\xD0\xB5\xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB5",
            data: "location",
            width: "14%"
        }];
    if (role === "leader") {
        columns.push({
            name: "\xD0\x98\xD0\xB6\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB5\xD1\x80",
            data: "engineerName",
            width: "13%"
        })
    }
    columns = columns.concat([{
        name: "\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F (\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD.)",
        data: "slaDate",
        width: "4%",
        group: "\xD0\x94\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0",
        render: function (data, row) {
            var slaDate = data;
            slaDate = slaDate.split(' ');
            slaDate = {time: slaDate[1], date: slaDate[0].split('-')};
            slaDate = slaDate.date.reverse().join('-') + 'T' + slaDate.time;
            //\xD0\x95\xD1\x81\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x80\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC\xD1\x8F \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8C\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5 10 \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x83\xD1\x82 \xD0\xB8 \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x85\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB2 \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD1\x83\xD1\x81\xD0\xB5 \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD1\x82\xD1\x81\xD1\x8F \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB8 \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD0\xB7\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0\xD1\x87\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD, \xD0\xB2\xD1\x8B\xD0\xB2\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB8\xD0\xBC \xD0\xBA\xD0\xBD\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBF\xD0\xBA\xD1\x83 "\xD0\x9E\xD1\x82\xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x82\xD1\x8C"
            var minutes = Math.floor((new Date(Date.parse(slaDate)).getTime() - Date.now()) / 60000);
            var answer = "<p class='table-header-theme'>" + data;
            if (row.slaDateAmended) {
                answer += '<i class="material-icons inherit-font sla-blue-icon">access_time</i>';
            }
            answer += "</p>";
            if (minutes > 0 && minutes < 480) {
                slaDate = minutes > 60 ? Math.floor(minutes / 60) + '\xD1\x87 ' + minutes%60 + '\xD0\xBC' : minutes + '\xD0\xBC';
                answer += "<p class='red-badge'>" + slaDate + "</p>";
            }
            return answer;
        }
    },
        {
            name: "\xD0\xA1\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB7\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F",
            data: "createDate",
            width: "4%",
            group: "\xD0\x94\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0"
        },
        {
            name: "\xD0\xA0\xD0\xB5\xD1\x88\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD0\xB8\xD1\x8F (\xD1\x84\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBA\xD1\x82.)",
            data: "finishDate",
            width: "4%",
            group: "\xD0\x94\xD0\xB0\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0"
        }
    ]);
    var table = new materialTable("table_wrapper",
        {
            search: {
                placeholder: "\xD0\x9F\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB8\xD1\x81\xD0\xBA \xD0\xBF\xD0\xBE \xD0\xB8\xD0\xBD\xD1\x86\xD0\xB8\xD0\xB4\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x82\xD0\xB0\xD0\xBC"
            },
            tableClasses: [
                "tickets-table"
            ],
            columns: columns,
            ajax: {
                url: 'api/ticket/' + stateArr,
                pagePar: "page",
                sizePar: "size",
                page: page
            },
            afterRender: function () {
                var $tableRow = $('table.tickets-table tbody tr');
                $tableRow.each(function(index, value) {
                    // \xD0\xBC\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBD\xD1\x8F\xD0\xB5\xD0\xBC tr \xD0\xBD\xD0\xB0 a, \xD1\x87\xD1\x82\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB1\xD1\x8B \xD1\x81\xD1\x82\xD1\x80\xD0\xBE\xD0\xBA\xD0\xB0 \xD0\xB1\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBB\xD0\xB0 \xD1\x81\xD1\x81\xD1\x8B\xD0\xBB\xD0\xBA\xD0\xBE\xD0\xB9
                    $(value).children().unwrap().wrapAll('<a class="' + $(value).attr('class') + ' table-row" style="display: table-row" href="#ticket/' + $(value).data('id') + '"></a>');
                });

                var $module = $(".desc_clamp > p");
                $module.each(function (index) {
                    $clamp($module[index], {clamp: 3});
                });
            }/*,
            afterRowRender: function ($targetRow, row) {
                if (window.outerWidth < 400){
                    var $firstTD = $targetRow.find('td:first-child');
                    switch (row.ticketStateId){
                        case 0:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-0');
                            break;
                        case 1:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-1');
                            break;
                        case 2:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-2');
                            break;
                        case 3:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-3');
                            break;
                        case 4:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-4');
                            break;
                        case 5:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-5');
                            break;
                        case 6:
                            $firstTD.addClass('mobile-sla-6');
                            break;
                    }
                }
            }*/
        });
}
